headline: Micron (MU) Delivers Earnings Beat and Strong Forecast, Stock Outlook Brightens
summary: Micron Technology, Inc. (NASDAQ:MU) is one of the AI Stocks Every Investor Should Watch. On September 24, Barclays analyst Tom O’Malley raised the price target on the stock to $195.00 (from $175.00) while maintaining an Overweight rating.
